     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"We plan to issue annual benefit statements for active members at the end of September 2017.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "The statements will be sent to your home address and will include details of the pension you have earned to date and your estimated pension at age 60/65, as well as details of any Additional Voluntary Contributions (AVCs) you have paid. It will also include details of the value of your pension for Lifetime Allowance purposes.",
     "If you have registered for self service your benefit statement will also be available to view online through your self service account.",
     "For those who have paid AVCs, the annual AVC statements as at 31 March 2017 have been issued."
